title: Video: YOUTHCULT – Bored
content: Swedish outfit YOUTHCULT cropped up in October of last year and have kept things fairly under wraps since then. Still no identities attached to the project, and new video for recent track Bored doesn’t reveal anything more substantial either. As with their debut YOUTHC*NT EP, Bored straddles the middle ground between the epic, stadium suited rock of WU LYF and the beauteous, more elegant compositions associated with Manchester outfit MONEY. It’s a huge sound.
